detail.name: God Kamehameha
detail.effect:
[Permanent] If you have no Battle Cards, reduce the cost of this card in your hand by 1.
[Activate Main] Choose up to 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards with 30000 power or less and KO it.

[起動 メイン]相手のパワー30000以下のバトルカード1枚までを選び、KOする。
